<view class="container">
  <view class="header">
    <text class="title">热力学特性</text>
    <text class="subtitle">THERMAL PROPERTIES</text>
  </view>
  
  <view class="module-list">
    <view class="module-card" bindtap="goToSpectrum">
      <view class="card-icon">🌈</view>
      <view class="card-content">
        <text class="card-title">光谱指纹</text>
        <text class="card-desc">通过光谱分析识别危废成分特征，建立独特的"指纹"标识</text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-arrow">→</view>
    </view>
    
    <view class="module-card" bindtap="goToThermal">
      <view class="card-icon">🔬</view>
      <view class="card-content">
        <text class="card-title">热行为指纹</text>
        <text class="card-desc">分析危废在不同温度下的热力学特性和反应规律</text>
      </view>
      <view class="card-arrow">→</view>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>